      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted NIH must agree with experimental NIH within 15% at the validation operating point. Pressure head must agree within 10% across all 5 COU operating points.",
      "rationale": "NIH agreement 7% at nominal operating point. Pressure head agreement mean 4.2%, max 8.7% across all 5 points. Both criteria satisfied. Acceptance criteria are defined in terms of output magnitudes and do not include criteria for verifying the linearity precondition of the damage accumulation model."
